&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACritical+and+Miscellaneous+Essays+%28Carlyle%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Sanders, Charles Richard;  et al., eds. (1985). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://carlyleletters.dukejournals.org/cgi/content/full/10/1/lt-18380110-TC-AC-01#FN6\"><i>The Collected Letters of Thomas and Jane Welsh Carlyle. Vol. 10: 1838</i></a>. Durham, N.C.: Duke University Press. pp.&#160;5\u20136, footnote 6. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0822306115\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0822306115\">0822306115</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">3 July</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Collected+Letters+of+Thomas+and+Jane+Welsh+Carlyle.+Vol.+10%3A+1838&amp;rft.place=Durham%2C+N.C.&amp;rft.pages=5-6%2C+footnote+6&amp;rft.pub=Duke+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft.isbn=0822306115&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcarlyleletters.dukejournals.org%2Fcgi%2Fcontent%2Ffull%2F10%2F1%2Flt-18380110-TC-AC-01%23FN6&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACritical+and+Miscellaneous+Essays+%28Carlyle%29\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Gordan, John D., ed. (1953). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=K3c4AAAAIAAJ&amp;q=%22Later+in+1838+he+wrote+a+preface+for+%22&amp;dq=%22Later+in+1838+he+wrote+a+preface+for